Invocation Name: f. three lazy booker
Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill is a voice-powered alternative to using F3 Functional Fitness at Totem Lake's booking website. Gym sessions are a paid service, but the use of this skill to simply book a session is free. Visit in person or call to speak to a representative for details. (425) 898-4003
